{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 89031,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どうせ飲めんのだから」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Since you can’t drink it anyway.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89032,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あら、平気よ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh, I’m fine."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89033,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　お供えものは最後に誰かが頂いてもいいのよ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It’s okay if someone eats the offerings at the end, you know?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89034,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「今完全にお供えものっつった！？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Did you just say 'offerings' out loud?!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89035,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「やーっ、日光さん、いらっしゃーい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yay! Hikkoku-san, welcome!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89036,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ええ、どうも」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, thank you.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89037,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "カフェの部屋に日光とカオスが遊びに来ていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Hikkoku and Chaos had come to visit the cafe room."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89038,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「日光さんはカオスと違って、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Unlike Chaos, Hikkoku-san"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89039,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　人間にもなれるから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "can also become human,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89040,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　お茶の淹れ甲斐があるわー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "so it’s worthwhile to make tea.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89041,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おうおう、ひどいこと言ってくれるな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh, oh, you say terrible things.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89042,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「カオスも人間になれたら良かったのにねー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It would be nice if Chaos could become human too, huh?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89043,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それにしても驚きました。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Still, I’m surprised."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89044,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　まさか、こうして三人が揃う日が来るとは」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "To think a day would come when the three of us would gather like this.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89045,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「以前にカオスとは会ったことがあるので、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Since I’ve met Chaos before,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89046,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いずれはこんな日が……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I thought a day like this would come someday..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89047,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　と思ったこともありましたが」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I even thought so at times.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89048,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さーさー、まずは飲んで下さい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Now, now, please drink first.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89049,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ、カフェのお茶ですか……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Ah, the cafe’s tea, huh...?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89050,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "日光は朗らかに微笑みながら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Hikkoku smiled brightly,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89051,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "湯飲みを受け取る。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and accepted the teacup."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89052,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「カフェのお茶は、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The cafe’s tea"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89053,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　私達パーティーの癒やしでしたね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "was the comfort for our party, wasn’t it?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89054,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「本当に……本当に、懐かしいです」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Truly... truly nostalgic.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89055,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「んっ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Mmm...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89056,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89057,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……はあ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Hah.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89058,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふふ、あの頃と変わっていない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hehe, nothing’s changed since those days.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89059,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89060,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「？　どうしました？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"? What’s wrong?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89061,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ずるい。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That’s unfair."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89062,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　同性でもうっとりするくらい綺麗……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "So beautiful it makes even someone of the same sex enchanted...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89063,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はい？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89064,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「お前はまたそーゆーことを言う。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"You say that kind of thing again."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89065,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なんだ、また神にでも会いに行くか？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "What, are you going to see the gods again or something?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89066,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いーえっ、もうすっかり懲りました」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, I’ve completely learned my lesson already.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89067,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89068,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「みんなには一度謝らないと、ね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I have to apologize to everyone at least once...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89069,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はあ？　なんのこっちゃ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh? What are you talking about?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89070,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「私達が神に会って、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"When we met the gods,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89071,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それぞれの願い事を叶えてもらった日のこと」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and each had our wishes granted.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89072,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「みんなは魔王や魔人を倒す力や、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Everyone wished for the power to defeat demon lords and demons,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89073,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　全知をって願ったのに……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "or for omniscience... but"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89074,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　私だけ美貌を下さいって……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I alone asked for beauty...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89075,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「突然、あんなこと言っちゃって、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Suddenly saying such a thing,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89076,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ごめんなさい！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I’m sorry!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89077,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔王や魔人をなんとかする為に集まったのに、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"We gathered to do something about demon lords and demons,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89078,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　最後の最後であんなこと言うの……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and at the very end you say that kind of thing..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89079,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ひどい裏切りだって……思うから」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It feels like a terrible betrayal... that’s what I think.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89080,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89081,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ま、別にどうでもいいだろ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well, it doesn’t really matter.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89082,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「集まった……つったって、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Even if we gathered..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89083,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　元々そんな真面目なパーティーでもねぇしな」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "it wasn’t like it was a very serious party to begin with.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89084,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なあ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89085,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ええ、あの場で何を願うのもカフェの自由です」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, Cafe was free to wish for whatever at that place.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89086,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それに……あまり良い目にはあわなかったと……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Besides... I’ve heard, subtly from Chaos, that it didn’t turn out very well for her...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89087,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　カオスにそれとなく程度ですが聞きました」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89088,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そんな人を責めるような言葉は",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I do not have words to blame such a person.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89089,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　持ち合わせていません」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89090,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「う、うん……二人とも、ありがとう……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Y-Yeah... thank you both...\""
    }
  ]
}

